snippet.title: "I Kept The Money" AH Admits She LIED About Donating $7M to Charity

In this video, Film Streak showcases that Amber Heard initially lied about donating $7M to charity where Johnny Depp exposed her during court. Now, she is rumored to admitting that she actually spend the money on herself instead of donating it to a good course. What do you think about this?
